类 CellCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.mapreduce.CellCreator

  • @InterfaceAudience.Public
public class CellCreator
extends Object
    Facade to create Cells for HFileOutputFormat. The created Cells are of Put type.
